New package cli/output/ contains: result.go (Result types), presenter.go (Presenter interface + Render), plain.go (PlainPresenter), color.go (ColorPresenter), json.go (JSONPresenter), ansi.go (ANSI constants + helpers), tty.go (IsTerminal + SelectPresenter). New subpackage cli/commands/ contains one file per command plus command.go (interface + types) and helpers.go. cli/registry.go has the Registry. cli/cli.go retains Run + RunWithRender + stripGlobalFlags.